wikipedia_page.main: Stella Marian Minter Mitchell (born 21 July 1947) is a British former swimmer. Mitchell competed in two events at the 1964 Summer Olympics. At the ASA National British Championships she won the 220 yards breaststroke title four times in 1963, 1964, 1965 and 1966.
